    <details>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>Miss Hilda Martindale CBE (1875 - 1952), first established The Hilda Martindale Educational Trust in order to help ‘Women of the British Isles whose intention it is to fit themselves for some profession or career likely to be of use or value to the community’.</p>
<p>Today, the Trust is ran and administered by the Council of Royal Holloway, as part of the University of London. The Council is responsible for appointing Exhibition Trustees who make awards on behalf of the Trust.</p>]]></Value>
    </details>
